OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784294319
OL,3,CToddler killed by driver using TikTok
OL,4,Cat wheel 'beautiful' say parents
OL,6,FIn a statement, Chloe and her husband
OL,7,FDaniel said: "No parent should ever
OL,8,Fhave to outlive their child, let alone
OL,9,Flose them in the most horrific way
OL,10,Flike we did.
OL,12,F"It splits your life into two - the
OL,13,Fbefore and the after - and we wouldn't
OL,14,Fwish for anyone to live in this after.
OL,16,F"The Finley shaped hole that has been
OL,17,Fleft in both our lives and hearts will
OL,18,Fnever be filled.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784294319
OL,3,CToddler killed by driver using TikTok
OL,4,Cat wheel 'beautiful' say parents
OL,6,F"Knowing how full of life he was and
OL,7,Fhow much he still had to experience in
OL,8,Flife, makes his death impossible to
OL,9,Faccept. We will forever continue to
OL,10,Fhonour and remember him for the
OL,11,Fbeautiful little soul that he was."
OL,13,FDuring sentencing, the court heard
OL,14,Fthat Iliev had previous penalties for
OL,15,Fspeeding and using his mobile phone at
OL,16,Fthe wheel.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
