OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784294319
OL,3,CToddler killed by driver using TikTok
OL,4,Cat wheel 'beautiful' say parents
OL,6,F"We don't get to take him to his first
OL,7,Fday of school, watch him in his first
OL,8,Fschool nativity or sports day. We
OL,9,Fwon't ever know who he would have
OL,10,Fbecome as an adult, we can only guess
OL,11,Fwhat kind of future he would have had.
OL,13,F"We never get to see him get married
OL,14,For have a family of his own. His
OL,15,Fentire life was stolen from him for
OL,16,Fthe most senseless of reasons."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/5
